Pounds 30.7m to Pounds 34.6m. Sales of Gerber computerised signmaking
systems declined however, from Pounds 16.6m to Pounds 15m.
Ultramark, the self-adhesive materials manufacturing side, recorded a 20 per
cent sales increase from Pounds 4.58m to Pounds 5.48m.
