FT  17 MAR 93 / The Budget (Government Statements): Relief on samples
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
In future VAT relief will be available wherever a sample is sent. Currently
samples sent to, for example, television and radio stations who are not
customers are taxed at cost. The main beneficiaries are expected to be the
producers of CDs, tapes, etc.
