FT  17 MAR 93 / The Budget (Government Statements): Detailed changes in VAT
regime
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
THE annual registration limit for VAT was increased from Pounds 36,600 to
Pounds 37,600 from midnight last night. The limit which applies to
acquisitions from other EC countries will also be increased to Pounds
37,600. The limit for those considering cancellation of their registration
will be increased from Pounds 35,100 to Pounds 36,000 from May 1.
